    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically like-new and drives like a total dream, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look!",
