    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal engineering. Featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, this example boasts crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to eliminate any potential for timing deviation. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with documented subframe reinforcement, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement. Finished in its original factory coating with zero paint depth variance, the vehicle sits on pristine Style 67 forged alloys. The M-variable limited-slip differential operates silently, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory spec. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
