    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original, high-gloss factory finish which has been further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found across the entire bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assistance sensors, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. The engine bay is concours-clean, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather exposure. The tires are recent high-performance replacements with near-full tread depth. This is not just a well-kept car; it is a time capsule for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 45800.0,
